---
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Inoue Dojo | Inoue-juku"
  description="Introducing the Inoue Dojo (Inoue-juku) in Atsubetsu-ku, Sapporo. A full-contact kumite training class that builds children's physical and mental strength, producing Hokkaido-wide champions in both the junior and general divisions."
  lang="en"
  path="/en/dojo/inoue/"
>
  <section class="dojo-list">
    <div class="page-container">
      <div class="section__title-area">
        <span class="section-label">INOUE DOJO</span>
        <h1 class="section-title">Seishinkai Karate-do Federation — Inoue Dojo</h1>
      </div>

      <p class="detail-page__lead">
        [Seishinkai Atsubetsu — Inoue Dojo]<br />
        The Kawashimo Karate Class began activities in April 2001 (Heisei 13) at the Genshirin Hall in Higashi-Atsubetsu.<br />
        After 10 years there, it moved its base to the current Higashi-Atsubetsu Children's Hall in August 2011 (Heisei 23).<br />
        The Kawakita Karate Class started in October 2009 (Heisei 21) as a class under direct headquarters control, and came under the management of Inoue-juku in October 2016 (Heisei 28).<br />
        <strong
          >In January 2023 (Reiwa 5), a dedicated dojo — the "<a
            href="https://youtu.be/bqi8972NRXE"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener">Inoue Dojo</a
          >" — was completed in Atsubetsu-Nishi, and the Kawakita and Higashi-Atsubetsu classes were merged into it.</strong
        ><br />
        If you can't make it to the Inoue Dojo, please consider the nearby <a
          href="/en/dojo/shiroishi/">Kawashimo Branch</a
        >, <a href="/en/dojo/shiroishi/">Kita-Shiroishi Branch</a>, <a
          href="/en/dojo/atsubetsu/">Atsubetsu-Minami Branch</a
        >, <a href="/en/dojo/atsubetsu/">Momijidai Branch</a>, or <a
          href="/en/dojo/atsubetsu/">Shin-Sapporo Branch</a
        >.<br />
        Inoue-juku places particular emphasis on building children's physical strength and mental resilience, and also serves as Seishinkai's full-contact kumite training class — it has produced Hokkaido-wide champions in both the Junior and General divisions.
      </p>

      <h2 class="detail-page__heading">Karate that builds a heart that won't lose, a spirit that won't break</h2>
      <table class="table">
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <th>
              🌟Inoue Dojo<br />
              Address: 4-13-23 Atsubetsu-nishi 4-jo, Atsubetsu-ku, Sapporo
              <a
